content-Type: application/json

{
  "title":"Testing",
  "boardId":"BOARD_ID"
}

###get boards list
GET http://localhost:5000/api/lists/BOARD_ID

###update list
PUT  http://localhost:5000/api/lists/LIST_ID
content-Type: application/json

{
   "title":"Updated List"
}

###delete list
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/lists/LIST_ID

###reorder lists
